title: Curve Wave by Liz Claiborne for Women 3.4 oz Eau de Toilette Spray
description: Introduced in 2005.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: COVERGIRL Smoothers Concealer Neutralizer 730, 0.14 Oz
description: Whether you need to conceal a little or a lot, this conditioning concealer with botanicals such as ginseng, vitamin E and chamomile will help your skin look smooth. Dermatologically-tested formula glides on easily to help cover dark circles, fine lines and other imperfections.

title: Remington CI5219 Instant Curls Ceramic Hair Curling Iron, 3/4 Inches
description: This instant curling iron delivers high ceramic heat and protects against damage. it provides smooth, shiny, long lasting curls with less damage.
